window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nexus is a hotspot for monsters and for some reason, they think I can do something about it.</p> <p>Ruby's got a special talent for disrupting magic and it's been causing problems her entire life. When she's recruited by the Special Monsters Unit, she finally discovers a use for her ability—and gets embroiled in a supernatural mystery that might destroy the world.</p> <p>Includes previously released titles:</p> <p>- Special Monsters Unit</p> <p>- Hidden Monster Ruins</p> <p>- The Monster King</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
